      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>Miracles of <persName ref="PRS10618ZaraB"/> which form part of his 
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7748TaammerZB">hagiographic dossier</ref>. The number of miracles may vary from 
               the core transmission of 26 miracles to 42 or more in other versions. The inclusion of a significantly greater number of miracles 
               may have occurred due to the merging of traditions relating to another saint with the same name.</p>
         </abstract>
